most_recent.text: Mushy and disgusting. Spend the extra $0.50 and get Annie's. Never have I ever had mushy gross noodles with Annie's
most_recent.title: Not the same mac and cheese we grew up with

most_recent.text: The flavor of Kraft Mac & Cheese never gets old. I have enjoyed it for the last 54 years. We add it to all of our holiday meals as a side dish. The cheese flavor has not changed, that I have noticed, in those years. If I’m not up to making home made Mac, this is always my go to.
most_recent.title: Kraft Mac & Cheese

most_recent.text: The kids and I both love kraft Mac n cheese. This was always a quick go to for lunch or a side if I knew the kids didn't like what I cooed that night
most_recent.title: Kids love it

most_recent.text: Perfect amount if cheese. Very good flavor and taste. Super easy to make. Would recommend to everyone. Easy! Quick meal!
most_recent.title: The Best MC

most_recent.text: I honestly can’t remember how it tasted or how the quality was because it has been a really long time. I just remember it was good.
most_recent.title: good

most_recent.text: I use this product when I’m wanting to make a quick meal. I it’s super easy to make and delicious. I like to throw in some hamburger or tuna once in a while and it really makes for a fast cheep meal.
most_recent.title: Simple

most_recent.text: Kraft macncheese goes with almost anything. Making it the most versatile food you could possibly buy. Here is something I recently learned. I knew you could mix it with butter or milk. But recently I was out of both and asked Google for a substitute and behold macncheese made with cream cheese and it is so delicious.
most_recent.title: Amazing.

most_recent.text: Taste awesome. My son loved it and he is a very picky eater. So that's a plus. Really enjoyed the flavors and the packaging
most_recent.title: Macaroni

product_description.downstream_description: Kraft Original Macaroni & Cheese Dinner is a convenient boxed dinner. Kids and adults love the delicious taste of macaroni with cheesy goodness. Our 7.25 ounce mac and cheese dinner includes macaroni pasta and original flavor cheese sauce mix, so you just need milk and margarine or butter to make a tasty mac and cheese dinner kids love. With no artificial flavors, no artificial preservatives, and no artificial dyes, Kraft macaroni and cheese is always a great family dinner choice. Preparing macaroni and cheese is a breeze. Just boil the pasta for 7-8 minutes, drain the water and stir in the cheese mix, milk and margarine or butter. Now you can have your Kraft mac and cheese and eat it too.
